oing anthropogenic degradation of Cerrado habitats observed in recent decades.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Dos Santos, Aline Jung", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Vieira, Thiago Bernardi", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Faria, Karina De Cassia", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/ceabb6145f4f0bd24abb1cfb651d6ef4", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/c5e98ceb7d3074e827749b2da5e002292b634662a65197c7bfe6945e8a547e59", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/EQSCFQGV", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/EQSCFQGV", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/730f50544cd52904c8c42b79ed3059a3!/b293456-295932", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "8", "pages": "720-730", "title": "Basic and Applied Ecology", "volume": "17"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/ceabb6145f4f0bd24abb1cfb651d6ef4"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:EQSCFQGV"}, {"identifier": "10.1016/j.baae.2016.09.004"}], "communities": [{"id": "batlit"}, {"id": "biosyslit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid_type": "recid", "pid_value": "13462153"}}]}}, "title": "Effects of vegetation structure on 